Preheat oven to 350 degrees F. Mix cream cheese, milk, mayonnaise, Gravy Mix and 1/2 cup each of the mozzarella and pepperoni in large bowl until well blended. Spread in 9-inch glass pie plate sprayed with no stick cooking spray. Sprinkle with remaining 1/2 cup cheese and 1/4 cup pepperoni. Bake 25 minutes or until heated through and cheese is melted.